<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Refund & Return Policy</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #b5bfa1;
            background-image: url("/images/pattern.png");
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: 20vh;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20vh;
            background: white;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #222;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }

        .email {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .email:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/nav', { user: user }) %>


        <center>
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Refund & Return Policy</h1>
                <p>
                    Due to the personalized nature of our products, we <strong>do not offer refunds, exchanges, or
                        returns</strong> unless:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The product is <strong>damaged upon arrival</strong></li>
                    <li>There is a <strong>manufacturing defect</strong></li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    If your order is eligible for a claim, please submit your request within <strong>3 days</strong> of
                    receiving the product. Claims must include <strong>clear images</strong> as proof.
                </p>
                <p>
                    For all refund or return inquiries, please email us at:
                    <a href="mailto:support@customwear.co.in" class="email">support@customwear.co.in</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </center>

        <%- include('partials/footer', { user: user }) %>

</body>

</html>